{"tid":1212473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地聽我講","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T00:33:48.000Z","uid":77237,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf4db1e966c0f820cec51c15768748588d6c6b1","tid":1212473,"uid":77237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:55:59.000Z","msg":"唔好再硬碰啦！啲裝備完全唔同等級，真係會死人架。<br />\n同埋衝到入去係咪真係可以得到想要既野？<br />\n就算得，當我地衝到入去，咁之後點？坐係入面吸煙？<br />\n挨得幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n理性少少，佢地有槍 我地連拎舊磚都要咁大風險。<br />\n今晚係幾分鐘開一槍，已經放軟晒手腳架啦。<br />\n癲起上黎掃射，我地又可以點？<br />\n<br />\n對唔住，我好無用。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請各義士三思，唔想再有人白白犧牲。</span><br />\n<br />\n利申：今日放假係屋企訓左一日"},{"pid":"de547b6381427b43258409632bc39c1d0ba75151","tid":1212473,"uid":77237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:00:32.000Z","msg":"求下你地，唔好有事"},{"pid":"ed42d2738168268dd462f8eafd3e86d6750ba87e","tid":1212473,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:38:53.000Z","msg":"你繼續訓啦"},{"pid":"8ad16e5773f24645a2c92267f10c3ae2e21ad79c","tid":1212473,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:39:56.000Z","msg":"你長眠不起啦"},{"pid":"572435976a3aa170012ea5d35e8044692ad1430c","tid":1212473,"uid":77237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}